{"tid":727471,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"發現到鍾意去行山嘅好多都係低端人口","createTime":"2018-07-03T04:52:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-03T14:48:18.000Z","uid":123613,"like":7,"dislike":147,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"097117be894e53e9cf3cdc2a256b1483e29ec561","tid":727471,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T04:52:47.000Z","msg":"鍾意行山嘅，一係成班冇工返嘅廢中廢老，一係就搵錢搵得唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n識親幾個又係鍾意去行山嘅人，全部都搵唔過15k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當你星期日行完，行完梗係攰啦，星期一返到公司，老細見到你仲係未夠精神，點升你職加你人工呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋啲行山撚成日話想relax吓，無非係逃避現實，放假有時間點解唔打多份part time，又或者搵嘢學增值自己呀<br />\n<br />\n你話11 12月好天行山就冇所謂，一年四季都行就真係低端人口，琴日有人俾雷劈死，低端人口又少咁件啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42c615d7cb234568f35d8df42be0aeeb5a7a6554","tid":727471,"uid":20998,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T04:55:48.000Z","msg":"下個劈死你"},{"pid":"a250fb65b01721c71cc5028286a7063cbb01d75b","tid":727471,"uid":123613,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T04:55:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2269090787ed8328f855b016638f8850b922b79","tid":727471,"uid":16061,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T04:56:15.000Z","msg":"琴日個位都窮呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8ed50c0210b9b54ca0a4a41b9a9eb8dbbddefb6","tid":727471,"uid":176366,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T04:57:42.000Z","msg":"講嚟講去 你都係想講行山係原罪啫<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"793efba1cdc672d9ed4d38790bd741062b0f1178","tid":727471,"uid":143572,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T04:58:36.000Z","msg":"行下港島睇下布力徑同陽明山莊班住戶"},{"pid":"dc1ac6e31337e8dc